3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - GANs are a popular topic in AI research, and the paper proposes a new method for training them. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper's focus on image generation and visual quality also suggests a connection to graphics research. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper's use of auto-encoder based GANs and its focus on training stability and convergence could also be relevant to the neural computing community.
